data.description: Welcome home to this meticulously cared for 3 bedroom, 2 bath single-story home. New HVAC New Hot water heater!  Ideally located for your convenience. For military personnel or veterans, this home is conveniently situated near military bases, making your daily commute a breeze and its in close proximity to a variety of retail options. With its open floorplan, this residence promises a spacious and inviting atmosphere for you and your loved ones. This home is the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours today!
